metadata.name: LowPolyDollsBTC002
metadata.description:
LowPolyDolls collection is a glb format 3D model sold exclusively on the NFT Marketplace.
Each model is made of different colors or shapes, so no two models are the same.
They are designed in low polygon for ease of use on a variety of platforms.
The models contain bone armatures, so they can be used in the Metaverse as avatars.
